- Instructions Quiz # 2

- User will enter a value to withdraw

- When user enters -1 then the "Transaction is ended"

- When user enters a value higher than the input value then it will be "Insufficient funds! Your current balance is: 
  (balance value)"

- When user enters a valid inpue value then the input value will be subtracted from the entered balance value, hence, 
  "Withdrawal successful! Your new balance is (balance value)"

- When user balance is 0 then "Your balance is zero. No more withdrawals can be made."
